opendial.plugins

Class ParseValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • opendial.plugins.ParseValue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Value>, Value

    public class ParseValue
extends java.lang.Object
implements Value
    Representation of a dependency parse of a particular utterance. The parse contains the sequence of words (after tokenisation) together with their POS tags and labelled relation to their head.
    Author:
    Pierre Lison (plison@ifi.uio.no)
